languages.text: "Вовсе нет! Просто я... всегда мечтала стать для кого-то единственной и неповторимой. Но жизнь научила, что мы не всегда получаем желаемое".
"Not at all! It's just that I... I always wanted to be someone's one and only, but life has taught me that we do not always get what we want."

languages.text: “没有这回事！只是……只是我一直希望，能成为某个人心中独一无二的存在，只可惜……人生不如意的事情十有八九。”
languages.original_text: "Not at all! It's just that I... I always wanted to be someone's one and only, but life has taught me that we do not always get what we want."

languages.text: « Pas du tout ! C'est juste que... j'ai toujours rêvé d'être le seul et unique amour de quelqu'un, un jour. Mais s'il y a bien une chose que j'ai apprise, c'est qu'on n'a pas toujours ce qu'on veut dans la vie. »
languages.original_text: "Not at all! It's just that I... I always wanted to be someone's one and only, but life has taught me that we do not always get what we want."

traits.speaker: CassiaCompanion

languages.text: «¡En absoluto! Es solo que... siempre había querido ser la única persona para alguien, pero la vida me ha enseñado que no siempre tenemos lo que queremos».
languages.original_text: "Not at all! It's just that I... I always wanted to be someone's one and only, but life has taught me that we do not always get what we want."

languages.text: 「そんなこと！ただ…私はいつも誰かの唯一無二の存在になりたいと思っていたんです。しかし、人生は必ずしも自分の望むものが手に入るとは限らないことを教えてくれました」
languages.original_text: "Not at all! It's just that I... I always wanted to be someone's one and only, but life has taught me that we do not always get what we want."

languages.text: "Ganz und gar nicht! Ich bin nur ... Ich wollte immer jemandes ein und alles sein, doch das Leben hat mich gelehrt, dass man nicht immer bekommt, was man will."
